(Cybertron's moons were not rock.  They were like Cybertron, metal.  You can 
easily tell that from looking at it and when Unicron takes it apart, both of 
'em that is.  The scale of the Transformers differs with inconsistencies.  
They've been portrayed as being from 20 feet and to 60 or 80 feet, sometimes 
in the same episode.  Most people I know say they average 20-60 feet though)
